  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>List the basic concepts involved in house wiring</item>
<item>Define the terms thermal hazard and shock hazard</item>
<item>Describe the effects of electrical shock on human physiology and their relationship to the amount of current through the body</item>
<item>Explain the function of fuses and circuit breakers</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
