<definition id="fs-id1172101793967">
<term>thermal hazard</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172099501602">hazard in which an excessive electric current causes undesired thermal effects</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-id1172101727117">
<term>three-wire system</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172101920492">wiring system used at present for safety reasons, with live, neutral, and ground wires</meaning>
